      <section>
         <indexterm>interface board</indexterm>
      </section>
      <section>
         <p>The interface board is mainly used to provide analog and
digital inputs and outputs to the system that are not supported by
the original SUVT controller.</p>
         <p>The following functions are implemented:<ul>
               <li>
                  <p>Sensing of input, output and bypass voltages and currents (selection
is made through different plug-in boards) <ph otherprops="UL">â€“
bypass sensing is only active for UPS systems with bypass transformers</ph>
                  </p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>Status information for switches, contactors and temperatures
of transformers</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>Four individual fan monitoring inputs (static bypass switch,
transformers)</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>External connection board</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
      </section>
